channel.title: What can I do with this acc?
channel.description:
finished my exams so got 3 and a half months off. I get sooo bored during the day so i've taken up some of my time with a new hobby, but i'm thinking i could get back in to RS with this new graphical update coming soon, but i have no idea what i can do with my acc that would be fun.
any ideas? cb stats below. My cb level is either 90 or 91. [URL=http://imageshack.us][IMG]http://img144.imageshack.us/img144/3838/ttttnu5.jpg[/img][/URL]

Ohh, I forgot about all that bs.

[/quote]

Yeah well to others 64m is alot. The most I’ve ever had was no more then 8.5m in my bank.
